channel.title: Help! Help me now!
channel.description: Hi guys, well I have a 637/639 private server! i mixed the eclipse server with a Quantum client and Im trying to change the ip and make a webclient. Please help me! I have Team Viewer 7 and Skype (ali.abid331). If someone helps me, (I am willing to give them a lvl 72 rs account). Just help me! Im getting sick and tired of this! Im trying to find localhost, 127.0.0.1, and 0.0.0.0 for weeks and I cant find it anywhere. What should I do?????????? :confused: :confused: :confused: :confused:
